metadata.name: Alpha Flyers #1
metadata.description: Alpha Flyers is a group for NFT traders. The collection contains 333 flyer passes as the membership pass into the club. As a holder, you'll have access to our trading live stream where we demonstrate and discuss all the nuances of NFT trading, answer every question you might have about NFT trading directly in the voice channel. If you are feeling lazy, no problem, copy trade us in high-probability setups, and you'll see profit.
